high_descs: Turn around and walk past the diningtable and walk into the dining room to reach the left side of the diningtable.
Pick up the potato from the table.
Turn around and reach the fridge.
Cool the potato in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to exit the room and walk past the table and turn left to reach the bathroom and face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled potato in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the dining room next to the bedroom, near the diningtable.
Walk towards side of the dining room and pick a potato.
Turn right and slightly move towards the fridge.
Place the potato in the refrigerator by opening it, then close it.
Now pick the vegetable from the refrigerator and head to the bathroom crossing the living room by turning left and go to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink of the bathroom.
anns.task_desc: Place the potato in the SinkBasin of the bathroom by keeping it in the refrigerator.
